sentences.sContent: Rescue workers carefully clean an oil-soaked northern gannet bird at a facility in Fort Jackson, Louisiana.
sentences.sContent_eng: Rescue workers carefully clean an oil-soaked northern gannet bird at a facility in Fort Jackson, Louisiana.
sentences.sCn: 救援人员在路易斯安娜州杰克逊堡（ Fort Jackson）的一处救援场所仔细地清理一只浸透了油污的北塘鹅。

trans.tranOther: a large sea bird that lives in large groups on cliffs
